WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:01.547
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:01.547 --> 00:00:02.549
Praise the Lord.

00:00:02.549 --> 00:00:04.400
Thank you for joining me today.

00:00:04.400 --> 00:00:09.422
Well, we see that Canada has chosen their leader.

00:00:10.835 --> 00:00:22.870
I saw this coming several weeks ago, but I did not want to come out and try to discourage the believers there.

00:00:23.560 --> 00:00:26.790
I was like, 'Let's stand in faith that we can turn this thing.

00:00:26.790 --> 00:00:31.760
' And when I was in prayer yesterday with you all in that video, I saw the people crying.

00:00:31.760 --> 00:00:35.771
I saw Canadians crying because of the way the election went.

00:00:35.771 --> 00:00:36.869
They were weeping.

00:00:36.869 --> 00:00:38.423
I saw women crying.

00:00:38.423 --> 00:00:45.920
I saw people upset because of the turnout—believers that were upset about how their nation was going.

00:00:45.920 --> 00:00:49.715
And so if you go back and watch that, that's what I was seeing.

00:00:50.150 --> 00:00:52.325
I saw an uprising.

00:00:53.273 --> 00:00:56.147
People were upset about the turnout.

00:00:56.147 --> 00:00:59.679
Some people were saying, 'Hey, we're going to stand for what we want to stand for.

00:00:59.679 --> 00:01:12.711
' And there was an uprising in the Christian community in the days ahead because of the liberal beliefs and the liberal way they were wanting to take your nation.

00:01:14.004 --> 00:01:17.560
I saw the same thing going on in Australia.

00:01:17.910 --> 00:01:21.497
But there were little fires; they weren't big fires.

00:01:21.497 --> 00:01:26.159
I saw little fires in Queensland, Australia.

00:01:27.659 --> 00:01:31.611
I don't know what that was all about, but people were upset and they were rising up.

00:01:31.611 --> 00:01:39.200
They were rising up against the government and the decisions that were being made because they didn't like the way it was turning.

00:01:39.600 --> 00:01:49.590
As we see this, I told you I saw the barrels, those whiskey barrels rolling down from Canada into America because of the trade.

00:01:49.590 --> 00:01:57.954
I saw a global depression hitting the economy of Canada in the days ahead, similar to America.

00:01:57.954 --> 00:02:10.400
But then I saw that British Columbia wanted to stand out on their own because they wanted to be a part of the digital platform and all the things that are going on.

00:02:10.400 --> 00:02:15.840
I don't know if that's later on, but I saw this, so I don't know the timing of it.

00:02:16.594 --> 00:02:23.800
I'm just piecing together what I've gotten in prayer, bringing it out to you to give you hope that there will be a revival in Canada.

00:02:23.800 --> 00:02:30.296
It will come out of a great pressure, but there will be a major revival in the days ahead.

00:02:30.628 --> 00:02:35.973
I'm telling you all, the best is yet to come for the body of Christ concerning the harvest of the souls.

00:02:35.973 --> 00:02:40.505
So now what we do is pray for your leaders.

00:02:40.970 --> 00:02:52.613
Like I said, it was because of the body of Christ—the preachers not having a backbone in Canada and not preaching an uncompromising word—is what I was seeing.

00:02:52.613 --> 00:02:58.354
Remember I told you all I went in the spirit and I was praying with you a couple of weeks ago and I saw the preachers.

00:02:58.354 --> 00:03:13.154
I saw a lukewarmness in the churches, and the Lord said because of this lukewarmness, we're praying and we're upset about the politics, but the problem is we're not preaching the gospel in the churches that causes the culture to change.

00:03:13.154 --> 00:03:17.080
Because as the church goes, so does everything else.

00:03:17.080 --> 00:03:21.608
As the preachers don't stand on the word, so does everything else.

00:03:21.608 --> 00:03:26.152
The Lord warned me and even told me this is a wake-up call.

00:03:26.152 --> 00:03:38.253
We have a reprieve in America, a four-year window of Trump, and he even told me, 'We're wanting everything to be on Trump's shoulders to fix America.

00:03:38.253 --> 00:03:40.969
' Well, it's on America; it's on him now.

00:03:40.969 --> 00:03:55.919
But the bottom line was when I saw the sticky substance, this oily honey coming off the preachers' mouths, and cockroaches were coming in and out of the mouths and laying upon the lips of the preachers in America.

00:03:56.319 --> 00:03:59.645
I saw babies across the land with diapers on.

00:03:59.645 --> 00:04:01.280
And the Lord warned me.

00:04:01.280 --> 00:04:05.200
He said, 'The preachers are not preaching the meat of the word.

00:04:05.200 --> 00:04:08.879
They're preaching a milk gospel to the people.

00:04:08.879 --> 00:04:21.052
' And this is what's wrong with America, because the preachers are not preaching an uncompromising word that teaches people how to live by faith and to grow up strong—the ABCs of faith.

00:04:23.919 --> 00:04:29.966
So the babies were all across the land, but it wasn't just America; it was going across the whole world.

00:04:30.320 --> 00:04:39.776
This is a global problem where people need to wake up and preach the gospel the way it needs to be preached and not this compromising, lukewarm gospel.

00:04:40.400 --> 00:04:53.493
The Lord warned me this was coming and that people needed to have a backbone like a crowbar because what is coming is going to shake the world.

00:04:53.493 --> 00:04:55.973
We see fruit of it now.

00:04:55.973 --> 00:05:13.410
We pray for South Korea because I saw a communist party trying to rise up in Korea—as bad as North Korea—that it would try to be a little bit, a little bit, and it equals a lot.

00:05:15.551 --> 00:05:16.510
Do you see what I'm saying?

00:05:16.510 --> 00:05:25.804
It wasn't just all at once; it was like a frog in a pot being boiled and cooked alive and it didn't even know as the temperature rises.

00:05:27.627 --> 00:05:39.463
As the South Koreans adapted to it, the communistic party of China was influencing North Korea, and North Korea had its hand trying to influence and take down South Korea and Taiwan.

00:05:43.760 --> 00:05:46.880
As we see, they were trying to bring them in like a mother hen tries to bring in her chicks.

00:05:50.400 --> 00:05:56.480
That's what China was doing—trying to bring in those islands that they looked at as rebellious.

00:05:56.480 --> 00:06:02.560
'You're not underneath communism, and we need to bring you into the way we think.

00:06:02.560 --> 00:06:05.333
' It's a demonic way of thinking; it's bondage.

00:06:05.333 --> 00:06:08.907
And there's an iron curtain there that keeps Christianity out.

00:06:09.360 --> 00:06:17.080
The people of South Korea have become complacent, and so it was with so many other places where they don't want to lose their freedom.

00:06:17.080 --> 00:06:31.700
And the Lord told me, 'This is what's going to happen if the people don't rise up and take their authority, humble themselves and pray, and turn from their wicked ways, then they will hear from heaven and the Lord said he would heal your land.

00:06:31.700 --> 00:06:39.302
' I'm telling you all, it's a time like never before to be serious, looking at the signs of the times.

00:06:40.471 --> 00:06:41.670
So what do we do now?

00:06:43.220 --> 00:06:44.656
Canada's gone left again.

00:06:44.656 --> 00:06:46.273
We pray for revival.

00:06:46.273 --> 00:06:50.891
We pray that Australia goes better.

00:06:50.891 --> 00:06:52.148
We pray for South Korea.

00:06:53.102 --> 00:06:54.444
They're coming up really quick.

00:06:54.444 --> 00:06:57.280
And so, we pray for America.

00:06:57.280 --> 00:06:59.919
We pray for our economic situation.

00:06:59.919 --> 00:07:06.040
People say, 'Brandon, you know, in that video yesterday, there were so many people that agreed about number three.

00:07:06.040 --> 00:07:07.893
' I told you to pick one, two, or three.

00:07:07.893 --> 00:07:16.100
