00:07:34.815 --> 00:07:39.298
People interceding just like Abraham—people interceding and praying for the window.

00:07:39.298 --> 00:07:43.720
As the watchman on the wall, I am warning you of what's coming: shortages of food and goods.

00:07:50.640 --> 00:07:52.640
Well, 'we don't need China's stuff.

00:07:52.640 --> 00:07:55.691
' Folks, it's bigger than that.

00:07:55.691 --> 00:07:59.188
It's car parts.

00:07:59.188 --> 00:08:11.413
I saw people not being able to fix their cars, chips for the cars, things that were very tied to computers and our electric grid.

00:08:11.413 --> 00:08:14.366
I saw major power outages coming.

00:08:14.834 --> 00:08:17.200
Have I not warned you of this?

00:08:17.200 --> 00:08:24.960
Clear back in the summer of last year, I said I've seen major cyber attacks coming from China.

00:08:26.194 --> 00:08:28.400
I warned you back in July.

00:08:28.720 --> 00:08:40.640
I saw people without electricity in some cities for three weeks because of some kind of hack or computer problems.

00:08:40.862 --> 00:08:47.660
