00:09:27.137 --> 00:09:46.679
I have seen these two countries in meetings—major meetings about bringing troops over, bringing them out of the Western bloc because America has suppressed them—North Korea because of communism and all the things that are going on with how they treat their people.

00:09:46.679 --> 00:09:54.580
Well, Russia was saying, "Hey, you join up with us and we will bring you into the BRICS.

00:09:54.580 --> 00:09:57.226
We'll bring you into the BRICS.

00:09:57.226 --> 00:10:00.960
" So what we're seeing right now, I saw in visions.

00:10:01.320 --> 00:10:02.862
